caption.text:
Avenue of Stars

On the first day I arrived in Hong Kong, my friend @jfw19 told me that I should go to Avenue of Stars (because this is a must place to visit when you come to Hong Kong. And I found a article told that there is a show called "Symphony of Lights". But, after waiting for one-and-a-half hours, the show was not like I had expected. .
.
So, this is the photo I got around there.
.
#explorehongkong #explore

The Difference In Culture

In Indonesia, we taught to treat everyone as we want to be treated. We smile and say "thank you" after someone helped us. But, after several days in Hong Kong, I think it's hard to find these manners here. Even the shopkeepers won't say any kind of words when we got our payback. .
.
